content: Hello Mister Heine, my name is Maria Mamani from Bolivia. Thanks for inviting me to see the apartment in Munich. Let's talk about the rental price.
name: Maria Mamani from Bolivia

content: Thank you for your interest in my apartment, Maria. Based on our discussions, I would like to propose a rental price of 800 Euros per month. This is a fair market rate for a 25 square meter apartment in Munich. What is your counter-offer?
name: Heinrich Heine
